{"tid":2357281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反骨仔彭斯譴責示威者闖入國會","createTime":"2021-01-07T10:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T14:32:52.000Z","uid":316329,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f08a3ba868aab7eb8c891f8d32940e19474e2c4e","tid":2357281,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"美國副總統彭斯譴責示威者闖入國會山莊觸發衝突，形容今日是黑暗的一日。 彭斯批評示威者沒有獲得勝利、暴力亦永不會獲勝。彭斯表示，國會現時已經安全，呼籲議員繼續進行確認大選各州選舉人投票結果程序的聯席會議。 參議院共和黨領袖麥康奈爾形容，示威者嘗試干擾國家的民主但失敗而回，參議院將繼續確認美國大選勝選人的資格。參議院民主黨領袖舒默表示，襲擊國會的不應被稱為示威者，而是本土的恐怖份子，並不代表美國。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-07-2021/69397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-07-2021%2F69397&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z0x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=c352b784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-07-2021/69397</a></span>"},{"pid":"160d828d3598fc2ff927cd7090ce0a22f8324d51","tid":2357281,"uid":316329,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:10:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔又炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d8f54678689152737254a2ec84ce115d447ce0","tid":2357281,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"投登了"},{"pid":"3152364dfb8e21e4dadf0e4c8fd651755616a4f8","tid":2357281,"uid":242537,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/135668729_10224996710169012_8236382625218813093_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=825194&amp;_nc_ohc=Htay47ylkdwAX9UA9RY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=a64783ab55c04bdd68183542bf02ce14&amp;oe=601C05E4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F135668729_10224996710169012_8236382625218813093_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D82519